    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>✦ A Story in the Stars ✦</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025870/extras/202c7d86fd29ddf46aa91abdf561f754.poster.avif?t=1761908438\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025870/extras/202c7d86fd29ddf46aa91abdf561f754.webm?t=1761908438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025870/extras/202c7d86fd29ddf46aa91abdf561f754.mp4?t=1761908438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Play as <i>???,</i> a mysterious character who wakes to an unfamiliar world with too many questions, and not enough answers. Meet the residents of the Orrery, uncover their stories, and figure out what <i>???</i>'s got to do with any of it. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>✦ Features ✦</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025870/extras/10dc736f2844f5e59d48dbc8026edd66.poster.avif?t=1761908438\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025870/extras/10dc736f2844f5e59d48dbc8026edd66.webm?t=1761908438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025870/extras/10dc736f2844f5e59d48dbc8026edd66.mp4?t=1761908438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">    <strong>Interactive Storytelling!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Every room is a recreation of a mythology, which means every room has a unique mechanic that relates to their story in some shape or form. Work your way through each one and learn a little more about the story of the stars alongside our hero!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">    <strong>Mystery!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Learn the story behind our strange hero, whose very identity seems to be shrouded in unknowns. Why does it seem like everyone else seem to know exactly who they are, and who is that really who they're meant to be? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">    <strong>Mythology! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025870/extras/30c9dd42924b1082783db8f75594960e.avif?t=1761908438\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025870/extras_big/30c9dd42924b1082783db8f75594960e.avif?t=1761908438 width=800 height=355 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Lovingly crafted re-imaginings of classic Greek protagonists and creatures that are scattered amongst the stars of western horoscopes. Catch glimpses of interactions between them, and have your own little conversations with them as well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">From Made with Cookies to you, we hope you enjoy our game!</p>",
